Achievements.Name: Wrap It Up
Achievements.Description: Complete a case on any difficulty.

Achievements.Name: San Amaro's Finest
Achievements.Description: Complete a case on Hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Maximum Pain
Achievements.Description: Clear ten rooms of criminals while in slow-mo.

Achievements.Name: Knock Knock
Achievements.Description: Knock down a criminal while sliding into a room.

Achievements.Name: Boom Town
Achievements.Description: Neutralise three or more criminals with one Stinger grenade in the same room.

Achievements.Name: Super Cop
Achievements.Description: Finish three operations, losing less than ten health points in each.

Achievements.Name: Wave Rider
Achievements.Description: Survive five waves in Lockdown mode.

Achievements.Name: Hang Ten
Achievements.Description: Survive ten waves in Lockdown mode.

Achievements.Name: Operator
Achievements.Description: Achieve a kill with a side-arm, a tactical weapon and a grenade in the same room.
